      "content": "i just don't see how slowing down helps. it's like i'm running on a treadmill that's going too fast. no matter how much i rest, the machine just keeps pulling me back into the same mess. it feels less like a struggle i can win and more like a glitch i can't fix. it just keeps looping. it's exhausting to even exist like this.",
